Subject: [PATCH] K-distance knee finder with  Derivative-Based Method,
 Significant Knee Selection, Outlier Handling

---
 src/Lidar/ESP/DBSCAN_lidar.ino | 44 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++--
 1 file changed, 42 insertions(+), 2 deletions(-)

diff --git a/src/Lidar/ESP/DBSCAN_lidar.ino b/src/Lidar/ESP/DBSCAN_lidar.ino
